 net.","year":-1520},{"id":"reckzC3Np81lXPI25","ref":"Job.19.7","text":"Behold, I cry out of wrong, but I am not heard: I cry aloud, but there is no judgment.","year":-1520},{"id":"recw33vVqFbQpoezy","ref":"Job.19.8","text":"He hath fenced up my way that I cannot pass, and he hath set darkness in my paths.","year":-1520}]}
